foia:ReliedUponStatute.foia:ReliedUponStatuteInformationWithhel: Any portion of cockpit voice recording (CVR) or the portions of a transcript of a CVR that the Board did not find relevant to an investigation.

Any information relating to Board participation in foreign aircraft accidents, where the country conducting the investigation has not issued its report or 2 years have not elapsed from the date of the accident.

foia:OtherDenialReason.foia:OtherDenialReasonDescriptionText: Not a proper FOIA request for some other reason

foia:PersonnelAndCostSection.foia:FootnoteText: Personnel and offices that search for responsive records are not included in the count for full-time FOIA employees.

foia:BacklogSection.foia:FootnoteText: Due to the complexity, request may not be processed within 20 days.

foia:ProcessedRequestComparisonSection.foia:FootnoteText: One request processed retroactively during fiscal year.
